lore: WHAT THE !@#$ ARE YOU LOOKING AT? WERE YOU EXPECTING SOME KIND OF EPIC STORY IN THESE LINES? ABOUT HOW A HIGHER POWER CARVED ME INTO A ROCK? NO, YOU PIECE OF !@#$. THAT'S BULL!@#$. I DON'T KNOW WHAT THE IDIOTS WHO WROTE THIS WERE THINKING. IT !@#$ES ME OFF THAT HUMANS ARE SO USELESS. ANYWAY. GO !@#$ YOURSELF.
menagerieDialog: YOU COULDN'T !@#$ INTO YOUR OWN HANDS IF THEY WERE SEWN TO YOUR ASS.
